{"type": "article", "id": 10111, "title": "Chloé 新香水 Chloé Eau de Toilette", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-28T07:24:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235536ZT0tHz4QE5ADoCf9.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tChloé 将于今年 7 月推出新香水 Chloé Eau de Toilette ，香水主打白玫瑰香，融合了栀子花，佛手柑，柠檬香味以及麝香，蕴含着温柔和清新的女人味。在外观设计上，采用了方形透明玻璃瓶，色调上采用嫩粉色和白色，看上去充满了浪漫和柔软。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355354JzLElC2FG9MZ5fK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355359PSAHGtMd5m8j7ZK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}